      body: 'Professional services principals are often the only person who knows how something is done. That works — until it doesn\'t. Process Independence means turning tacit knowledge into documented, repeatable systems your team can run without you.',
    },
    questions: [
      { text: 'When we repeat a process more than twice, we document it so anyone on the team can follow it.', type: 'freq' },
      { text: 'Core recurring tasks — billing, client onboarding, compliance checks, reporting — have a documented process anyone can follow.', type: 'slider' },
